title: Ronald S. Gibbs, MD and Jane Holtz Gibbs Endowed Fund for Obstetrics and Gynecology
description: To provide faculty support for education of residents, research in infectious diseases or family planning in the Department of Obstetrics and Gynecology at the University of Colorado Anschutz Medical Campus.
